SOLUTION

solution is the citizen who applies the winning rule to the ARC test input and produces the answer
once rule_search has identified the rule that explains all the example pairs, solution takes the rule and applies it to the unseen test input
the result is fadriel's answer to the ARC task

observe 0_quseptit.rana
observe fadriel_spatial_arc2.zc
observe parietal_deep.rana
observe rule_search.rana
observe grid_state.rana

the 7 properties of solution:
1 ENERGY zero at idle, peaks during answer production
2 PHASE zero
3 SPIN zero
4 CHARGE neutral
5 COHERENCE one
6 COUPLING zero with everything except parietal_deep and rule_search
7 OBSERVER zero

VERB receive_rule
accept the winning rule from rule_search

VERB apply_to_test
take the unseen test input and apply the rule to it
the rule is a transformation; the input is a grid; the output is the transformed grid

VERB emit_answer
hand the resulting grid to grid_state and to whatever upstream system requested the ARC solution
fadriel has answered

a solution is not a guess
a solution is the disciplined application of a rule that was verified to work on examples
fadriel's ARC answer is correct or incorrect; it is not opinionated
the substrate has either found a rule that explains everything or it has not
